{"tid":269975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本周後期天朗氣清 連續3日高見33°C","createTime":"2017-06-04T04:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T10:04:16.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d313beeb7a3af7bfaf78f4f3d4f6edaffcc750","tid":269975,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:47:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>本周後期天朗氣清 連續3日高見33&deg;C</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發 <br />\n<br />\n2017-06-04 12:03:34 HKT<br />\n<br />\n今日禮拜日，今早將軍澳區及港島東區都有零散驟雨，而天文台預測，現時影響廣東的低壓槽會在未來一兩日逐漸減弱，本港的天色將會好轉。預料副熱帶高壓脊會在本周中期向西伸展，屆時本港將帶來普遍晴朗及酷熱的天氣，預料周四至周六連續三日高見33&deg;C，大家往戶外活動記得要保充足夠水分，同埋做好防曬措施。<br />\n<br />\n帶定遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2c7db64620f7053ab73be40e9b041e59e73a74","tid":269975,"uid":115987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:49:12.000Z","msg":"香港連天氣都咁濕鳩<br />\n6月頭熱到咁"},{"pid":"01d6c887c52521e22066708a41927caa327e637d","tid":269975,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"雷雨呢...?"},{"pid":"ec0b1a8c25c7ff7145daa3d4919bc00c432b8bde","tid":269975,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:04:16.000Z","msg":"帶定遮都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}